The Vibration Cell is the part of a vibroweapon that causes it to vibrate. It is an essential part of any vibro weapon because the damage they deal is significantly less if there is no vibration.

Better vibration cells can be fitted into the weapon to make it vibrate faster and deal more damage. The top of the range cells are able to make the blade vibrate so hard that it can slice limbs just by touching them, even without the wielder having to chop or slice.
